strings:
<voice_0x01000DA9><se_low>King Trode: Hm, we can't get in like this.
Jessica, can you get rid of these thorns
with some of your hocus pocus?

<voice_0x01000DAA><se_high>Jessica: I guess I can give it a try.
Let's see...
<voice_0x01000DAB><se_high>Jessica: There! Just don't ask me to get rid of all of them, okay!?

<voice_0x01000DAC><se_high>Jessica: My magic may be powerful,
but it's not that powerful!
